org.fosstrak.reader.rprm.core.mgmt.alarm
Class FailedMemReadAlarm

java.lang.Object
  org.fosstrak.reader.rprm.core.mgmt.alarm.Alarm
      org.fosstrak.reader.rprm.core.mgmt.alarm.FailedMemReadAlarm

public class FailedMemReadAlarm
extends Alarm

FailedMemReadAlarm extends the Alarm class. Its receipt signals a tag user-memory read failure. The abstract model's AntennaReadPoint.failedMemReadAlarmControl data element controls the triggering of alarms of this type.
